{"_id":"izRQgBwyaNDyzTse","name":"Perception sauvage","permission":{"default":0,"q0cco5K29nzbsRLe":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Au niveau 18, vos sens vous confèrent la capacité surnaturelle de mieux percevoir les adversaires qui ne vous sont pas visibles. Quand vous attaquez une créature que vous ne voyez pas, ce crtière ne vous impose pas de désavantage aux jets d'attaques correspondants.</p>\n<p>Vous connaissez en outre la position de toute créature invisible dans une rayon de 9m, tant qu'elle n'est pas parvenue à se soustraire à votre perception par d'autres moyens et que vous n'êtes ni aveuglé ni assourdi.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Aventuriers p.219","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":2,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"k9pw5epARmIPzjiX","name":"Archétype de rôdeur : Explorateur de l'Inframonde","permission":{"default":0,"q0cco5K29nzbsRLe":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Très tôt, vous avez statué (compris diraient certains) qu'un véritable aventurier se forge dans les ruines ancestrales et les galeries infinies de l'Inframonde, avec leur faune héteroclite, les dangers innombrables, leurs richesses incommensurables et leurs mystères inépuisables.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Aventuriers p.222","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":2,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
